Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.57,0:00:10.67,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.36,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:37.55,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of the Eye of \Nthe Midnight Sun, Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:42.02,italics,naR,0000,0000,0000,,Asta was no match for his \Noverwhelming magical powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:44.81,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The one who came to Asta's rescue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:48.21,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,was none other than the captain \Nof the Black Bulls, Yami Sukehiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.32,0:00:53.44,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,In a breathless battle between \Nlight magic and dark magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:57.36,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta went beyond his limits and \Nclosed in for his counterattack.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.36,0:00:58.53,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:02.33,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you... harm Valtos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.71,0:01:07.04,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot allow people like \Nyou to harm my comrades
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:09.42,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:13.13,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Light Creation Magic: Light Whip of Judgment!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:19.64,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless to struggle!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.23,0:01:23.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The cave!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:27.94,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That nutcase has gone ballistic!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.09,0:01:40.99,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear... I held back most of my magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:43.33,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,but it's all really too fragile...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:46.66,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Both this world and you fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:51.63,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Master Licht!\NYour strength is practically divine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:56.30,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,If you felt like it, Master Licht, the Magic \NKnights would be no more than infants!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.30,0:01:59.45,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:17.82,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Light of Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.45,0:03:40.61,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,If you concentrate like that, you can \Nsense the ki of natural objects, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:43.57,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That way, you'll never get killed\Nby stuff like falling rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:48.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ki is awesome! Hooray for ki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:50.08,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ki is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:50.08,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:52.62,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:56.42,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Now take it up a notch and go after the \Nwhite-haired dude with the round eyebrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:57.76,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:04:00.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I think I could do that right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:05.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Because of my ki,\NI'm enthusiastic, energetic, and confident!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:07.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hope you're ready, Round Brows!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:10.25,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, scratch that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:11.23,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:15.44,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I told him that I'd show him the \Npower of a captain, so I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:17.08,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, if you did it, you'd die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:21.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But then what am I supposed to \Ndo with all this extra energy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:22.74,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Not my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:26.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You can tackle that scrawny line-faced dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:29.54,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:32.79,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since I've let loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:27.80,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Magic:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:29.89,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Cloaked
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:31.82,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Lightless Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:34.31,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:37.56,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,My magic is being drawn in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:40.94,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the power of dark magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:42.19,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:46.95,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I know that, it'll be \Nimpossible for you to get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:51.28,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you were in the middle \Nof some weird story,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:53.66,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,but that wasn't the end of it, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.09,0:05:58.51,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That grimoire means you're a citizen \Nof the Clover Kingdom, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.51,0:06:00.51,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Why attack your own country?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:22.98,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,You're wide open.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:29.78,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,He left himself wide open \Nso I'd let my guard down...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:32.49,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Yami Sukehiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.33,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,You are a worthy foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:44.88,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me. What's your real goal here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:51.59,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're a foreigner, I'm sure \Nyou've noticed them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.65,0:06:54.65,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,The distortions in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:58.40,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Some are on the brink of \Ndeath from starvation,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:07:00.91,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,but others have so much excess \Nfood that they throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:05.00,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,People are ranked by how much \Nor how little magic they have,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:10.18,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,but some have great magic, yet are \Ndiscriminated against for reasons of birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:15.43,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Some are hurt in the name of justice \Nbecause they were born in another country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:20.66,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,We were born from these distortions...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:23.42,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,In order to correct them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:26.33,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not seeing the point here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:30.72,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you trying to do the same \Nthing these distorted people do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:33.72,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sane?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:36.20,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Perfectly sane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:38.97,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Let me answer your sins with sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:42.02,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So you're gonna have it \Nyour way, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:44.48,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I like guys like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:45.86,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:48.90,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I hate your guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:23.09,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's with this battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:26.52,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the captain's
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:27.95,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,full power...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:33.61,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any magic. Can I \Nsurpass them, even if I train?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:39.06,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This guy, Yuno, and the Wizard King...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:48.17,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,To think that he has enough power to \Ngo head to head with Master Licht...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:51.92,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Master Licht! Please allow me to assist you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:57.05,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:08:59.76,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:02.60,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you wimping out, you dumbass?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:05.60,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I left that scrawny guy to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:08.31,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give guys jobs they can't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:12.32,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Do something about him in your own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.73,0:09:17.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:22.54,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... I'm going to become \Nthe Wizard King, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:25.27,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to get depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:28.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:32.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,First, I'll become the guy who beats you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:34.17,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get me twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.98,0:09:38.68,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Spatial Magic: Myriad Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:44.33,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,You may be able to see what's coming, \Nbut can you block all of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:09:59.36,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,One of them got through...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:01.87,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,This will go on forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:04.87,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Until you can't move anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:18.34,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,You dared defy Master Licht \Ndespite having no magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:20.24,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,You will pay with your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:29.23,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... I don't think I'm going \Nto last until he runs out of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:34.08,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I manage to repel his attacks, \Nat this rate, he's going to beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:38.28,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down and think... Do this my own way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:44.62,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,You threw away your only weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:46.87,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Have you lost your mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.51,0:10:51.88,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll take you \Nout with an extra-big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:09.64,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,He jumped into my space?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:28.81,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You just punched him in the face!\NYou're hilarious, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:31.05,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,You let your guard down again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.07,0:11:33.85,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:37.17,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,My attack was absorbed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:41.26,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,And I can't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.89,0:11:45.26,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Magic: Black Hole, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:48.76,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Magic: Dark Cloaked
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:50.89,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Black Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:10.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:13.33,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.68,0:12:15.08,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,You got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.48,0:12:19.97,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably within five meters. \NThe range is definitely limited,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:21.97,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,but to think there was a magic
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:24.44,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,that could absorb my own magic \Nand stop me from moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:28.66,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Dark magic is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:33.64,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,The one attribute that's the \Nnatural enemy of my light magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:38.66,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,However, dark magic is extremely slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.66,0:12:42.63,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Light has absolute speed, making them\Npolar opposites there, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.08,0:12:46.74,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you cloaked \Nyour weapon in darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:50.12,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,and created a combat style that uses \Nreinforcement magic to compensate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:55.99,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:58.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it sound like he's bragging?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:02.71,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what's up? You can \Nuse recovery magic, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:04.63,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So hurry up and heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:08.33,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,But while you're healing yourself, \NI'm going to get real close
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:10.31,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,and chop you up even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.69,0:13:16.35,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I'll admit it. You're the second person \NI've met with the power to defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.68,0:13:21.11,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,But I sadly cannot waste my time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:23.58,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What was that, punk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:25.32,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And whaddaya mean, the second?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.69,0:13:31.02,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I still have an ultimate enemy left who \Ninflicted this unhealable wound on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:36.07,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,the Wizard King, Julius Novachrono.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:41.25,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,This is currently my greatest magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:44.37,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Speed you cannot avoid...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:47.68,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,A spell with such a wide range and \Nhigh output that pulling it in
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:50.66,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,with that spell you used won't do any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:57.31,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,You will meet your end the moment I \Nrelease this, Captain of the Black Bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:59.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell he will!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:02.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Quit underestimating Captain Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:04.03,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:07.53,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's not good. \NThat's some insane magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:09.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:17.08,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Boy. You will also be punished for\Nhurting Valtos, and return that grimoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:22.34,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That's definitely a four-leaf for you... \NHis magical abilities are off the charts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:26.03,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Unless I catch him by surprise, \Nhe'll just dodge any slash at light speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:27.09,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:32.02,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave that up to the me \Nof five seconds from now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:34.85,main,Kid a,0000,0000,0000,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.59,0:14:36.81,main,Kid b,0000,0000,0000,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.17,0:14:38.75,main,Kid A,0000,0000,0000,,I was so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:39.77,main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,There, there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:41.56,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:45.57,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That should be everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:48.74,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare die, you old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:50.95,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up, old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:53.68,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to be some \Nimmortal monster hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:55.37,main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:14:59.75,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,N-No... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:07.51,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche, you're hurt really badly, too, \Nso you should worry about your own—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:08.72,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:11.86,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... I'm the one with\Nseniority here, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.69,0:15:18.52,main,Mage 1,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche's treatments will be done soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:19.50,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:25.23,main,Mage 1,0000,0000,0000,,Well, all of his wounds just \Nbarely missed his vital points.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.54,0:15:27.49,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,So he was lucky?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:29.24,main,Mage 1,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure. That just seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:32.52,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Then hurry up and treat the old hag, not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.52,0:15:34.03,main,Mage 1,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:38.21,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Old hag! Wake up already! Old hag—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:39.09,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Tone it down...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:43.96,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear you, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:45.46,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.83,0:15:47.09,main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:54.97,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Take my magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.21,0:15:58.66,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to save them, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:01.85,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:04.60,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I never said I'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:09.99,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,You changed... after meeting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:13.96,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Gauche.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:16.34,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:23.83,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You're joking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:27.13,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You said you could die?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:29.19,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Bring her back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:30.16,main,Mage 1,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:31.10,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:32.30,main,Mage 1,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:33.80,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie's going to be sad, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:35.38,main,Mage 1,0000,0000,0000,,She's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:37.80,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:39.22,main,Mage 1,0000,0000,0000,,She's not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:43.81,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You old hag! Stop being so misleading!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:47.24,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a monster hag, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:51.57,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I won't kick the bucket so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:56.39,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Relax and get over there, \Nyou sister complex freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:17:00.31,main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,Take my magic, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:01.48,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Mine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:02.64,main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Mine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:04.58,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,Please save Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:09.17,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Please use my magic, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:10.48,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:15.34,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry for being \Nviolent toward your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:26.33,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be of any help if I went.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:29.36,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:30.90,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:38.11,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,See? Everyone lives by supporting each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:39.54,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:45.14,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You just protect what you want to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:48.92,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, that'll help somebody out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:54.58,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I know what I have to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.58,0:17:56.49,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:57.42,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Erk...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:59.55,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Take me back to that cave!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:01.60,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,S-Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:03.81,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm your senior, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:06.57,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, even if we go back,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:09.37,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,are you going to be able to do anything \Nabout that blinding magic guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:11.31,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't stand a chance earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:13.32,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,so it's probably better to\Nwait for reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:16.15,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I thought of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:17.15,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:20.16,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Unless I'm wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:22.25,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:25.29,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be able to surprise \Nattack him with my spatial magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:30.21,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,People with powerful magic have force \Nfields of magic that appear around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:32.20,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to get that close.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:37.34,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, I moved way too \Nmany people really far today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:40.75,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I may only be able to use \Nmy magic one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.75,0:18:41.77,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:42.97,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:43.88,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Finral...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:46.36,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.53,0:18:52.87,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:55.30,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:57.94,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Magic:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:18:59.88,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Black Cocoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:02.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:05.71,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I've gone into defensive mode, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:07.66,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,It's hopeless. He's gonna kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:10.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?! How are you so calm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:14.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then! I'll just deflect it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:17.07,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. The swords will probably \Nbe all that's left of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:18.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.12,0:19:21.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then what should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:23.93,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Not give up until the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:25.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're just trying to act cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:33.81,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,To be completely honest,\Nthere's nothing we can do right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:37.82,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Grit your teeth and stand firm.\NThat's all we can do right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:44.82,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Yami Sukehiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:51.12,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, what the hell?! \NDid we come to the wrong place?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:52.71,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:54.83,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That's Yami's magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:58.84,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Gah! This has gotten way out of hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:04.59,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Light Magic: Ray of Divine Punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:07.78,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,He came.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:11.20,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:15.23,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Magic: Full Reflection!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:32.62,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how big or strong it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:35.17,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Mirrors reflect light!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:21:01.28,main,Veto,0000,0000,0000,,To think someone could wound Sally this badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.85,0:21:04.86,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I hate them. This is unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.06,0:21:11.51,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,This is annoying, but it\Nlooks like it's our turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:52.35,sign_33083_276_Petit_Clover_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,520)}Pe{\c&H3BC020&}t{\c&HE2AF0F&}i{\c&H3BC020&}t C{\c&HE2AF0F&}l{\c&H3BC020&}o{\c&H0E42D4&}ve{\c&H3BC020&}r
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.82,0:22:51.78,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.20,0:22:55.85,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Voice Change
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.93,0:22:54.26,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Voice Change.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.81,0:22:59.46,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,M-Marie's coughing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:01.12,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Did you catch a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.12,0:23:04.52,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,It was pretty cold in the cave! \NAre you all right, Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.52,0:23:07.07,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, my throat's just a little sore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:08.06,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.10,0:23:10.28,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,My voice sounds strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.27,0:23:15.49,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,M-My angel Marie's voice \Nsounds like Captain Yami's!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.49,0:23:19.66,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, Brother, \Ngo save Asta and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.07,0:23:22.71,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Take my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.04,0:23:24.73,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,The old hag's voice is weird, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:28.25,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I may only be able to use \Nmy magic one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.25,0:23:29.67,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, Finral?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.25,0:23:33.89,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, now my throat is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:35.70,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Your voice is cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.56,0:23:42.27,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I did it, Marie! Your big \Nbrother defeated the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.27,0:23:45.36,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I need to hurry back to Marie... \NWho the hell are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.36,0:23:47.57,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,No one said anything about reinforcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.57,0:23:50.61,main,gauche,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 36: "Three Eyes."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.57,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 36\N\N{\fs18} Three Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.61,0:23:52.95,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I might not be able to \Ngo back just yet, Marie.
